class_notes: Students must register for practicum course NRSG 609 Neonatal NP Practicum I
course_description: This course focuses on advanced assessment competencies and primary healthcare for low-moderate risk neonates and older infants up to age 2. Students explore collaborative practice models for resuscitation, stabilization and delivery room management.
prerequisites: NRSG 552 and NRSG 554 or equivalent transfer credit as prerequisites.
